allodb
  • Reference

A dummy table listing sites and species in ForestGEO's network.

This table relates the table of allometric equations by species with the table of allometric equations by site.

site_spp

Format

A data frame with 12 rows and 2 variables:

* `spp`: A character vector of species' names -- in lowercase.

* `site`: A character vector giving site names -- in lowercase.
